      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready for a dependable ride that's perfect for your daily needs! This car is in fair condition, showing some honest wear and tear from its time on the road, but it remains a solid, functional choice for anyone looking for value. It's been a reliable companion and is ready to keep going for its next owner!",
