      "description": "Hi there! I'm looking to find a new home for my reliable ride. It\u2019s been such a great car for me and is still in really wonderful shape! It drives super smoothly and has been well-loved, so it's definitely ready for many more adventures. I\u2019ve taken good care of it, and I think you\u2019re really going to love how it handles. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions\u2014I'd love to tell you more about it!",
