    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E46 M3 powered by the S54B32 inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and high-pressure double-VANOS variable valve timing. This unit delivers linear power up to its 8,000 RPM redline, mated to a 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a factory-spec M-Variable limited-slip differential. The chassis has been proactively addressed with subframe reinforcement plates, and the suspension maintains its factory geometry with refreshed bushings and dampers. Recent technical service includes a comprehensive valve shim adjustment and a rod bearing replacement to ensure long-term reciprocating assembly integrity. While the exterior shows minor patina consistent with enthusiast use, the drivetrain exhibits excellent volumetric efficiency and crisp throttle response. A driver-focused example ready for the B-roads.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
