    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This vehicle has been meticulously cared for and remains in impressive condition both inside and out. The exterior retains its deep luster, showing only the minor road wear expected of a well-loved car. Inside, you'll find a pristine, smoke-free cabin with premium leather seats that show minimal signs of use and no tears. All electronic features, including the infotainment system, navigation, and dual-zone climate control, function perfectly. Mechanically, this car is exceptionally sound; it comes with a fully documented service history and drives with the same precision and power it had on day one. Recent maintenance includes a fresh oil change, new brake pads, and a comprehensive multi-point inspection, ensuring it\u2019s ready for its next owner to drive away with total confidence. It strikes the perfect balance between luxury, performance, and daily reliability.",
